SUMMARY:MIDCAP FINL ISSUER TR — Investor Call #5
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, February 3\, 2026. Sign up: https://markets.jpmorgan.com/event_booking/loadEvent?eventToken=130165_b2497320-ba4d-429d-9281-4a69f8f114ad\nIssuer: MIDCAP FINL ISSUER TR\nRoadshow: www.netroadshow.com | Entry Code: MidCap2026 | Secure Link: www.netroadshow.com/nrs/home/#!/?show=6ffaa456\n\nDeal context:\nMidCap Financial Issuer Trust is arranging fixed income investor calls on February 2-3\, 2026 ahead of a potential offering of senior unsecured notes and/or junior subordinated notes via Rule 144A without registration rights. The issuer carries expected ratings of Baa2 (Stable) from Moody's and A- (Stable) from Kroll\, positioning this as an investment grade deal. J.P. Morgan\, Truist Securities\, and Wells Fargo Securities are coordinating the investor outreach\, with a NetRoadshow presentation available to qualified institutional buyers.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR